WEBVTT

00:01.668 --> 00:04.904
CARLA: Hey, Cheers is filmed
before a live studio audience.

00:04.904 --> 00:06.906
Afternoon, Woody!

00:06.906 --> 00:08.408
Oh, hiya, Mr. Twitchell.

00:08.408 --> 00:09.909
If it isn't Walter Q. Twitchell,

00:09.909 --> 00:11.911
the man who put the "nie" in weenie.

00:14.914 --> 00:16.916
You South Central Branch types

00:16.916 --> 00:18.918
are all alike--
wisenheimers.

00:18.918 --> 00:21.337
Good Lord, Miss Agnes!

00:23.339 --> 00:25.341
You're wearing your postal keychain

00:25.341 --> 00:27.343
and you're not on active duty?

00:27.343 --> 00:28.344
Well...

00:28.344 --> 00:29.846
That's a direct violation

00:29.846 --> 00:30.847
of postal regulations.

00:30.847 --> 00:32.348
I'm filing a report on you.

00:32.348 --> 00:33.850
Oh, yeah? Yeah.

00:33.850 --> 00:35.351
I'd love to see the supervisor's face

00:35.351 --> 00:36.853
when he calls me out on the mat

00:36.853 --> 00:38.354
and I whip out this little baby.

00:38.354 --> 00:39.856
Heh? Care to take a peep

00:39.856 --> 00:41.725
at the old French peeper here, Twitch?

00:41.725 --> 00:46.196
I warn ya, it's, uh, pretty hot stuff.

00:51.701 --> 00:53.703
You're a sick man, Clavin.

00:57.707 --> 01:00.210
(all laughing)

01:00.210 --> 01:02.212
What are you...?

01:02.212 --> 01:04.214
Oh, nice shiner there, Twitch.

01:05.715 --> 01:07.634
Yeah, they could never pass up

01:07.634 --> 01:10.136
a chance to sneak a peek
at Natalie in her nightie.

01:10.637 --> 01:12.138
TWITCHELL: Nightie?!

01:12.138 --> 01:13.640
Wasn't wearing anything I could see.

01:13.640 --> 01:15.642
Huh?

01:15.642 --> 01:17.644
TWITCHELL: Revenge is sweet.

01:17.644 --> 01:18.645
Here's your mail.

01:18.645 --> 01:19.646
Have a nice...

01:21.981 --> 01:25.401
(piano plays)

01:25.401 --> 01:27.854
? Making your way in the world today ?

01:27.854 --> 01:30.857
? Takes everything you've got ?

01:30.857 --> 01:33.860
? Taking a break from all your worries ?

01:33.860 --> 01:36.863
? Sure would help a lot ?

01:36.863 --> 01:42.252
? Wouldn't you like to get away? ?

01:42.252 --> 01:45.038
? Sometimes you want to go ?

01:45.038 --> 01:50.043
? Where everybody knows your name ?

01:50.043 --> 01:55.048
? And they're always glad you came ?

01:55.048 --> 01:57.050
? You want to be where you can see ?

01:57.050 --> 02:00.053
? Our troubles are all the same ?

02:00.053 --> 02:05.058
? You want to be where
everybody knows your name ?

02:05.058 --> 02:08.061
? You want to go where people know ?

02:08.061 --> 02:10.062
? People are all the same ?

02:10.062 --> 02:15.068
? You want to go where
everybody knows your name. ?

